channel.description:
[CENTER][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/lHYV02a.png[/img]
Hey Rune-Server! GenesisPVP is now back & better than ever! With recently added Dungeoneering that is sure to blow all of your minds, we're really hoping to hit the top spot. I mean, c'mon it's a long way to go for everyone, but it'll be our biggest and our only goal. The main point is that we take your ideas and suggestions into action, which is exactly what we do at GenesisPVP. With an Owner that actually listens to the players, not one of those that just sits back & does nothing and rarely ever visits the community. Not to mention we're also looking for some staff as we currently do not have any, so more reason for you to join. You might be thinking, hah! That's obviously old & they've probably got staff members by now, but this will only be removed once we have. But for now we are desperately looking for some staff members, if you're active, helpful... then it just might be your day!
